WEBVTT

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.480
especially from rural hospitals.

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:04.960
So we built our own towers,

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:07.616
created a wireless network

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:10.056
and linked clinics in Lilongwe,

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:11.280
Malawi's capital.

00:04:12.600 --> 00:04:15.480
(Applause)

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.200
With a team of engineers

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.496
working within a hospital campus,

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:25.176
we observed health care workers
use the system

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:28.416
and iteratively
build an information system

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:32.256
that is now managing HIV records